meta__dataSources: Epoch AI Monte Carlo models, Raymond James semiconductor research, TrendForce quarterly reports, SemiAnalysis teardown data
meta__schema__vendor: Chip vendor (NVIDIA, AMD, Intel, Google, AWS, Microsoft, Meta)
meta__schema__dieSizeMm2: Total die/package area in mm² (null if undisclosed)
meta__schema__estMfgCostUsd: Estimated total manufacturing cost in USD
meta__schema__estSellPriceUsd: Estimated sell price in USD (null for internal/cloud-only chips)
meta__schema__chipGrossMarginPct: Gross margin percentage (null for internal/cloud-only chips)
meta__schema__costBreakdown: Manufacturing cost components (logic die, HBM, packaging, test & assembly)
